Why do you need network access for this kind of paid app?
replyContent: Thanks for your feedback! This app supports both local photos and photos in cloud storage such as Google Photos, so we need to use network connection to download images and also handle errors gracefully if the photo can not be accessed due to network issue. Hope this addresses your concern.
